{"questionId":"11823","questionHtml":"<p>Find the particular solution to the original system, given the initial conditions of part (b).</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {100 = A + B + 10} \\\\   {50 = - A + B + 20}  \\end{array} \\Rightarrow A = 30{\\text{,}}\\,\\,B = 60\">\n  <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n    <mtr>\n      <mtd>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>100</mn>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mi>A</mi>\n          <mo>+</mo>\n          <mi>B</mi>\n          <mo>+</mo>\n          <mn>10</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </mtd>\n    </mtr>\n    <mtr>\n      <mtd>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>50</mn>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mi>A</mi>\n          <mo>+</mo>\n          <mi>B</mi>\n          <mo>+</mo>\n          <mn>20</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </mtd>\n    </mtr>\n  </mtable>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>A</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>30</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>B</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>60</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  x \\\\   y  \\end{array}} \\right) = 30{e^{ - t}}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   { - 1}  \\end{array}} \\right) + 60{e^{3t}}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   1  \\end{array}} \\right) + \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {10} \\\\   {20}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>y</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>30</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>e</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>−</mo>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>60</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>e</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>3</mn>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>10</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>20</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"11823","referenceCode":"EXM.3.AHL.TZ0.3f","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find the particular solution to the original system, given the initial conditions of part (b).","paper":"3","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"f","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5—Calculus","Topic 5—Calculus","AHL 5.1